&lt;section class=&quot;block sounds&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Sounds of the revolution...&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        The Most Highly Anticipated Obituary in the History of the World — Political Satire Targeting Trump&lt;br/&gt;
		&lt;i&gt;The Resistance&lt;/i&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7QH6OocW5ck&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
