        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;After taking control of Venezuela&#39;s entire oil industry, the Trump regime has cut off all oil supplies to Cuba, plunging the country into darkness and chaos. It doesn&#39;t appear that Donny 2-Dolls has any clear plan about what comes next. But apparently that doesn&#39;t matter, because he claims that he can do anything he wants with it and that he will &quot;take Cuba&quot; in some form.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;blockquote&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;I do believe I&#39;ll be…having the honor of taking Cuba&lt;p&gt;
