    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        No Kings Day #3 is March 28 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nokings.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
