&lt;section&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;tangerine&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center;font-size:4em;padding:1.2rem 0px;&quot;&gt;Impeach. Convict. Remove.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Kristi Noem out of DHS. Republicans sow chaos in Texas primaries and US boosts Russian oil sales. Trump regime&amp;#39;s plan to steal 2026 elections revealed. More ICE lies surrounding shooting of Ruben Martinez.&lt;/p&gt;
