                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G_WqgMg5Id0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-LegalEagle) Trump&#39;s insance plan to steal elections leaked&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pbs.org/newshour/politics/trump-says-hes-not-mulling-a-draft-executive-order-to-seize-control-over-elections-heres-what-we-know&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(PBS) Trump says he&#39;s not mulling a draft executive order to seize control over elections. Here&#39;s what we know.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
