&lt;section class=&quot;block info&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Keeping you informed...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Video evidence once again contradicts ICE claims surrounding shooting &lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/texas-ice-shooting-ruben-martinez-death-e7377deeae6ba9a42a31b7b03da14598&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
