    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/1Df84_KSZt-628.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;Footage of ICE shooting of Ruben Martinez&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/1Df84_KSZt-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;628&quot; height=&quot;493&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/1Df84_KSZt-200.webp 200w, /images/1Df84_KSZt-628.webp 628w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;From police body camera footage taken the night Martinez was killed.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://free-the-people.us/blog/posts/2026-03-01-week-in-review/&quot;&gt;Last week&lt;/a&gt;, we shared an &lt;a href=&quot;https://americanoversight.org/lawmakers-call-for-investigation-after-records-reveal-undisclosed-ice-shooting-death-of-u-s-citizen/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;article&lt;/a&gt; from ProPublica about the fatal ICE shooting of Ruben Martinez last year that was covered up until recently. This week, bodycam footage from the event was released.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Just like the shootings of Nicole Good and Alex Pretti, the video evidence contradicts statements made by the ICE-stapo agents. Just like the incident with Renee Good, one agent recklessly positioned himself in &lt;i&gt;front&lt;/i&gt; of the vehicle while another attempted to enter the vehicle, causing the driver to panic and gently accelerate while turning the vehicle to leave the scene. Just like the incident with Good, Martinez was shot three times at point-blank range. And just like the incident with Good, Martinez&#39;s killer, Jack Stevens, claimed that his actions were necessary to prevent a &quot;terrorist attack.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Federal agents have killed at least six people under the current Trump regime, and the initial reports made by these agents nearly always contradict the actual evidence from video and eyewitness testimony. &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
