&lt;section class=&quot;block the-bad&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Trump regime ends all greenhouse gas emissions standards &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pbs.org/newshour/science/watch-live-trump-zeldin-to-announce-end-of-scientific-basis-for-u-s-action-on-climate-change&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/AJQ3uLAn5r-800.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;Exhaust from a line of cars&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/AJQ3uLAn5r-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;345&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/AJQ3uLAn5r-200.webp 200w, /images/AJQ3uLAn5r-800.webp 800w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com/users/geralt-9301/?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=4767388&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Gerd Altmann&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com//?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=4767388&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Pixabay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Trump regime has brought an end to the rule backing every environmental regulation on greenhouse gas emissions. It is will known that carbon dioxide and other greenhouse gases endanger the public health and lead to climate change. This scientific fact led to the passage of the Endangerment Finding passed in 2009 that essentially codifies this finding into law. The endangerment finding is the central basis for all greenhouse gas emissions standards and laws.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Repealing this law will roll back emissions standards for cars and trucks, as well as power plants and oil and gas facilities. One the immediate targets is removing fuel efficiency requirements and restrictions on tailpipe emissions from cars and trucks. These restrictions have provided a boost to the electric car market, which the Trump regime is trying to destroy.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pbs.org/newshour/science/watch-live-trump-zeldin-to-announce-end-of-scientific-basis-for-u-s-action-on-climate-change&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(PBS) Watch: Trump, EPA&#39;s Zeldin announce end of scientific basis for U.S. action on climate change&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pbs.org/newshour/politics/trump-set-to-gut-u-s-climate-change-policy-and-environmental-regulations-white-house-official-says&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(PBS) Trump set to gut U.S. climate change policy and environmental regulations, White House official says&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;hr style=&quot;clear:both&quot;/&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
       Pam Bondi responds to criticism over her handling of the Epstein files with shouting and name-calling &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2026/feb/11/pam-bondi-democrats-epstein-hearing&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
