            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G7TeKNU_Dps&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-ProPublica) What really happened when USAID was cut&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
