&lt;section&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;tangerine&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center;font-size:4em;padding:1.2rem 0px;&quot;&gt;Impeach. Convict. Remove.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Minneapolis nominated for Nobel Peace Prize, Alex Pretti&amp;#39;s killers identified, and Kristi Noem may be impeached. Kennedy Center closing under Trump&amp;#39;s failed leadership. Trump regime is making plans to take control of 2026 elections. The real story behind Trump&amp;#39;s tariff madness.&lt;/p&gt;
