            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kristi Noem&lt;/b&gt; addresses the nation the day after her agents killed Renee Good. The podium has the phrase &quot;One of ours, all of yours&quot; written on it. This is a Nazi slogan linked to a 1942 incident where Nazi soldiers massacred an entire village in the modern-day Czech Republic in retaliation for the death of an SS soldier who had been terrorizing the village.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;After Noem lied to the public about the events leading to the murders of Renee Good and Alex Pretti by ICE agents who report to her, Democrats are telling Donny 2-Dolls to fire her. If he does not, they say they will file articles of impeachment.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;So far, Trump&#39;s bootlickers are (predictably) defending both Noem and the regime&#39;s actions. Time will tell whether these threats from Democrats will be taken seriously by either party or anything will come of them.&lt;/p&gt;
