&lt;section&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;tangerine&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center;font-size:4em;padding:1.2rem 0px;&quot;&gt;Impeach. Convict. Remove.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: ICE is not welcome in Minnesota, nor in the United States. The Trump regime still refuses to release the Epstein Files in violation of the law. ICE-stapo murders another in the streets. Trump&amp;#39;s dementia is getting worse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;

&lt;section class=&quot;block the-good&quot;&gt;
	&lt;h4&gt;The good...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Message from Minnesota: ICE not welcome here &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thegodpodcast.com/p/bless-the-minneapolis-general-strike&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/GVxI2EJtxZ-800.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;&#39;God&#39; watches over Minnesotans protesting ICE abuses in their state&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/GVxI2EJtxZ-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/GVxI2EJtxZ-200.webp 200w, /images/GVxI2EJtxZ-800.webp 800w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;50,000 people gather outdoors in -10&amp;deg;F weather to let the Trump regime know their ICE-stapo is not welcome on American soil&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;On January 23, temperatures in Minneapolis dropped to -10&amp;deg;F with wind chills reaching -20&amp;deg;F. Under normal circumstances, most people in the area would stay indoors, trying to keep warm. But these are not normal circumstances, and tens of thousands of Minnesotans filled the streets to protest the Trump regime&#39;s reign of terror and to demand the ICE-stapo agents who are threatening their very lives leave their state for good.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;blockquote&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;We will not rest until ICE is abolished and every one of these vile thugs are prosecuted for their crimes.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;figcaption class=&quot;blockquote-footer&quot;&gt;&quot;God&quot;&lt;/figcaption&gt;
		&lt;/blockquote&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thegodpodcast.com/p/bless-the-minneapolis-general-strike&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Letters from God) Bless the Minneapolis general strike against ICE in -10&amp;deg;F&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;hr style=&quot;clear:both&quot;/&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;

&lt;section class=&quot;block the-bad&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        More than a month after the deadline to release the Epstein Files has passed and less than 1% have been released &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2026/jan/24/legal-experts-epstein-files-release-congress&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;On November 19,  Congress passed a law called the &quot;Epstein Files Transparency Act&quot; that ordered the Attorney General to &quot;make publicly available in a searchable and downloadable format all unclassified records, documents, communications, and investigative materials in the possession of the Department of Justice&quot; that relate to Jeffrey Epstein within 30 days. That deadline came and went on December 19th. This week marked the passage of a full month since that deadline.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;So, has the Trump regime obeyed the law passed by Congress and signed by Donny 2-Dolls?&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;No. Less than 1% of the files have been released to date, and the few files that were released since the passage of the law are mostly documents that have already been released to the public previously. Despite going to war with Venezuela, threatening to take Greenland by force from our own NATO ally, and sending thousands of armed thugs into Democratic cities to terrorize and murder United States citizens right here at home, the Trump regime just can&#39;t seem to make people forget about the Epstein Files.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;This is a major issue for the Trump regime because Donny 2-Dolls ran on campaign promises to release the Epstein Files, and some of his sycophants have become slightly less ardent in their support of the Trump regime as he&#39;s continually refused to keep that promise.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;What can be done to force the Trump regime to obey the laws it has passed? There&#39;s not much that can make an immediate difference, but steady and ongoing legal pressure to force the regime to provide legal justification for its refusal to comply with the law and ongoing public pressure can eventually force the regime&#39;s hand. But it won&#39;t happen any time soon, and it won&#39;t be easy.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;
			&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/EU0kBVqNM38?si=2AEdYGnOXxhoWXi4&quot; title=&quot;YouTube video player&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allow=&quot;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2026/jan/24/legal-experts-epstein-files-release-congress&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(The Guardian) What else can be done to force Trump&#39;s DoJ to release all the Epstein files? Legal experts weigh in&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EU0kBVqNM38&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-LegalEagle) Trump DOJ in contempt of Congress&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
