&lt;section class=&quot;block the-ugly&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The ugly...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        ICE-stapo continues its murderous rampage &lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/immigration-enforcement-minnesota-4d1499fc5962ab880f3816259e04bdbf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;ICE-stapo agents gunned down another man on the streets of Minnesota on Saturday. Details are sketchy at the time of this writing, but video shows agents wrestling a man to the ground, repeatedly striking him on the head, and then shooting him dead. The man has been identified as Alex Jeffrey Pretti, an ICU nurse at a Minneapolis VA hospital. As with the killing of Renee Good, federal agents and the Department of Homeland Security have blatantly lied about the events, despite the fact that both shootings were captured on camera.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The killing is part of the largest immigration enforcement operation in the history of this country, but had nothing to do with immigration enforcement at all. Federal agents were not engaged in any specific immigration enforcement operations at the time, but were swarming the streets to square off against protesters in the hopes of instilling fear into the local community. This is a terrorist tactic aimed at intimidating people into accepting the Trump regime&#39;s refusal to follow the law or respect the Constitution.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;There is no place in this country for an organization like ICE, and there is no place in this country for the authoritarian Trump regime.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;
			&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/xsJhg3q11Qo?si=ZusUOK_Zl2uSp6m7&quot; title=&quot;YouTube video player&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allow=&quot;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;blockquote&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;Immigration agents are being instructed by Trump officials to violate the constitution. The Fourth Amendment provides protections against unreasonable search and seizures. But ICE agents have been told those constitutional constraints do not apply. A whistleblower revealed a secret ICE memo saying they do not need a judicial warrant to forcibly break into a home.&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;figcaption class=&quot;blockquote-footer&quot;&gt;Don Moynihan, &lt;i&gt;Can we still govern?&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;
		&lt;/blockquote&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
