                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/minnesota/live-updates/reported-shooting-south-minneapolis-federal-agents-protesters/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(CBS News) Federal agents fatally shoot another Minneapolis resident; Minnesota officials say feds deny access to shooting scene&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/immigration-enforcement-minnesota-4d1499fc5962ab880f3816259e04bdbf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(AP) Man shot during Minneapolis immigration crackdown has died, hospital record shows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
